  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         Cheetah
Scientific:   Acinonyx jubatus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     12 years
Weight:       65 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Fastest land animal at 120 km/h; cannot roar; purrs instead

Name:         Axolotl
Scientific:   Ambystoma mexicanum
Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

Name:         Hummingbird
Scientific:   Trochilidae
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Forest
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     5 years
Weight:       0.003 kg
Status:       Varies
Fact:         Only bird that can fly backwards; heart beats 1,260 times per minute

